headline: How Americans are using AI at work, according to a new Gallup poll
summary: American workers adopted artificial intelligence into their work lives at a remarkable pace over the past few years, according to a new poll.  In addition, majorities of those working in professional services, at colleges or universities or in K-12 education, say they use AI at least a few times a year.
